    <a href="https://www.facebook.com" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
    <a href="https://www.twitter.com" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/chi-tsang-779aa11a9/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
  </div>
  <div>
    Made by Chi
  </div>
  <div class="footer-copyright">
    You clearly <i class="fas fa-heart"></i> to drink if you got to this point.
  </div>
</div>
